---
import "./CardImplement.css";
---

<article class="round no-elevate p-0 wave">
  <div class="gfx gfx-implement" role="img" aria-label="A wireframe cube assembling itself edge by edge, suggesting a working system being built and shipped">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" aria-hidden="true">
      <!-- Front face -->
      <line class="edge e1"  x1="110" y1="130" x2="190" y2="130" pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e2"  x1="190" y1="130" x2="190" y2="50"  pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e3"  x1="190" y1="50"  x2="110" y2="50"  pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e4"  x1="110" y1="50"  x2="110" y2="130" pathLength="100" />
      <!-- Back face -->
      <line class="edge e5"  x1="150" y1="105" x2="230" y2="105" pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e6"  x1="230" y1="105" x2="230" y2="25"  pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e7"  x1="230" y1="25"  x2="150" y2="25"  pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e8"  x1="150" y1="25"  x2="150" y2="105" pathLength="100" />
      <!-- Connectors -->
      <line class="edge e9"  x1="110" y1="130" x2="150" y2="105" pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e10" x1="190" y1="130" x2="230" y2="105" pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e11" x1="190" y1="50"  x2="230" y2="25"  pathLength="100" />
      <line class="edge e12" x1="110" y1="50"  x2="150" y2="25"  pathLength="100" />
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="p-5">
    <h3 class="text-3 lh-2 fw-6">Implement</h3>
    <p class=" mt-2 text-1 italic">For startups and growing teams.</p>
    <p class="text-0 mt-2">You have a problem AI could solve. We work alongside your team to design, build, and ship it. Not a demo. Not a prototype destined for a shelf. A working system your people actually use.</p>
  </div>
</article>
